  "problemTitle": "그 정수의 개수를 구해줘",
  "bojProblemId": "28253",
  "infoHtml": "<thead><tr><th style=\"width:16%;\">시간 제한</th><th style=\"width:16%;\">메모리 제한</th><th style=\"width:17%;\">제출</th><th style=\"width:17%;\">정답</th><th style=\"width:17%;\">맞힌 사람</th><th style=\"width:17%;\">정답 비율</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>5 초 </td><td>1024 MB</td><td>148</td><td>33</td><td>26</td><td>34.667%</td></tr></tbody>",
  "bodyHtml": "\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<section id=\"description\"  class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2>문제</h2>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_description\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>두 정수 $L, R$이 주어졌을 때, 닫힌구간 $[L, R]$에 속하는 정수 중 정수 $X$를 <strong>포함</strong>하고 있는 정수의 개수를 구하시오.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>어떤 정수 $a$가 다른 정수 $b$를 <strong>포함</strong>한다는 것은 두 정수를 문자열로 보았을 때 $a$의 연속된 부분 문자열 중 $b$가 존재한다는 의미이다. </p>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"input\"  class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2>입력</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_input\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>첫 번째 줄에 두 정수 $L, R$이 공백으로 구분되어 주어진다. ($1 \\le L \\le R &lt; 10^{100000}$)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>두 번째 줄에 $X$가 주어진다. ($1 \\le X &lt; 10^{100}$)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>정수 $L, R, X$에 대해 $0$으로 시작하는 경우는 입력으로 주어지지 않는다.</p>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"output\"  class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2>출력</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_output\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>닫힌구간 $[L, R]$에 속하는 정수 중 $X$를 <strong>포함</strong>하고 있는 정수의 개수를 $998\\ 244\\ 353$로 나눈 나머지를 출력한다.</p>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t<section id=\"limit\" style=\"display:none;\" class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t<h2>제한</h2>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_limit\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sampleinput1\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>예제 입력 1\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"sampledata\" id=\"sample-input-1\">1 20\n3\n</pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sampleoutput1\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>예제 출력 1\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"sampledata\" id=\"sample-output-1\">2\n</pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sample_explain_1\" class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_sample_explain_1\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>닫힌구간 $[1, 20]$에 속하는 정수 중 $3$를&nbsp;<strong>포함</strong>하고 있는 정수는 $3$, $13$이다.</p>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sampleinput2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>예제 입력 2\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"sampledata\" id=\"sample-input-2\">100 200\n3\n</pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sampleoutput2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>예제 출력 2\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"sampledata\" id=\"sample-output-2\">19\n</pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<section id=\"hint\" style=\"display: none;\" class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2>힌트</h2>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_hint\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\"><section id=\"source\"><div class=\"headline\"><h2>출처</h2></div><p>Contest&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;BOJ User Contest&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;월간 향유회&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;월간 향유회 2023. 06.&nbsp;D번</p><ul><li>문제를 만든 사람:&nbsp;snrnsidy</li><li>문제를 검수한 사람:&nbsp;amsminn, chogahui05, djs100201, pjshwa, tony9402, utilforever</li></ul></section></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
